    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-09-14T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-09-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="525"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d525">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Bolet Peraza</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Foster</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Venezuela</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">New York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-09-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 14, 1892</hi>
                        </date>. (Received September 14.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The witness whose testimony is needed to libel steamer <hi rend="italic">South
                        Portland</hi>, armed and chartered to be used in hostility to my Government,
                    cannot reach New York until late tomorrow. Will you telegraph instructions to
                    detain vessel to enable me to present my proofs?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">N. Bolet Peraza.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
